Completely remodeled and completed in 2014. A state-of-the-art open floor plan, grand open kitchen/family room, and breakfast nook seating for 10. A master wing with extensive private outdoor covered patio, fireplace, infinite his and her master baths and closets designed for today's royalty. Gated circular motor-court for 10 cars with oversized 3-car garage. Extremely private with endless and breathtaking mountaintop views.

Contact @misslhommedieu or @bachiroueida for more information! @1518belair

@RaminDesigns designed & built this $23,500,000 Miami Beach mansion. Located in the exclusive Venetian Islands, this stunning waterfront home embodies the ideal combination of modern Miami Beach design, unobstructed views, outstanding outdoors for waterfront living, and deluxe amenities put together in a tasteful yet indulgent fashion. With 12 foot high ceilings, 6600 sq ft of luxury living space this home offers 6 bedrooms and 6.5 bathrooms.

See @RaminDesigns for more luxury homes!
